      <title>MSCI 通过剔除更多股票削减中国在指数中的比重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/msci-trims-china-s-presence-in-gauges-by-culling-more-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于北京方面的刺激计划未能阻止中国市场在区域基准指数中的影响力下降，MSCI 指数公司进一步下调了中国股票的评级，尽管该公司将更多印度股票纳入了其指数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/msci-trims-china-s-presence-in-gauges-by-culling-more-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 07:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中国市场持续低迷，资生堂下调全年业绩预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/shiseido-lowers-full-year-forecast-as-china-weakness-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本化妆品巨头资生堂公布，受主要中国市场持续低迷影响，该公司净收入出现暴跌，因此该公司大幅下调了全年利润预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/shiseido-lowers-full-year-forecast-as-china-weakness-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 07:21:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
